# Forbidden Patterns

- Business logic inside widgets
- Direct `SharedPreferences` usage in UI or domain
- Hardcoded secrets
- Silent catch blocks
- Untyped dynamic maps without model mapping
- Massive widgets (>300 lines)
- Repository bypass
- Circular provider dependencies
- God repositories
- UI-driven data transformations
- Shared mutable state outside StateNotifiers
- Framework leakage into domain
- Platform service calls from domain layer
- Hardcoded colors/durations instead of theme/`AppAnimations`

